{
  "stem": "20616.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, my bar mitzvah was not to be-- was not to be until later on the next year.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But because we were ready to emigrate, it was put ahead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My family wanted us to be together for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was an only child and of course, my grandparents wanted to be there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember that my bar mitzvah was the last time we all got together socially.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a very enjoyable occasion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was prepared for the bar mitzvah by the same teacher who-- religious teacher who prepared-- prepared my father for his bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was not a very well-liked teacher, not even a very good teacher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But he was an institution and we tolerated-- I was his favorite student for some reason or other.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, Werner always carries a book around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there was once when I accidentally had a book in my hand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Of course, after that, I made a point of always carrying books around when I went to religious school, and that impressed him very much.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And behind his back we, of course, we made a lot of fun of that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the gymnasum, while I was there, we also-- we were not hit as much as, but we also-- physical punishment was also par for the course.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And even if we didn't know our vocabulary in Latin or something, we were sort of pummeled and physically hit and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In religious school, things were a little different.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], occasionally he hit us and gave us a [GERMAN], a slap in the face.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we really must have done something quite badly.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
